      "question": "Find the class mark of the class interval 150-200.",
      "answer": "175",
      "solution": {
        "steps": [
          "Identify the lower limit (L) and upper limit (U) of the interval.",
          "Apply the formula: Class mark = (L + U) / 2."
        ],
        "derivation": "\\text{Class mark} = \\frac{150 + 200}{2} = \\frac{350}{2} = 175."
